name: City Bus
description:
Rai & Raka decided to continue their journey by bus to their destination.
They didn't know what the area was like, but anxious anticipation enveloped them.

Raka hopes it will be a very comfortable place to live.

Starting to get annoyed and tired of covering Rai because she expected to find his boarding house soon but when she arrived in this new city it turned out that she had to still look for it.

Raka tries to comfort his younger sister, believing that they will soon be found through the map Raka brought.

Will they find their destination at the next bus stop?
